      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 20 — Customer Onboarding Orchestrator\n\n**HubSpot custom properties to create:**\n- onboarding_status (text)\n- milestones_completed (number)\n- onboarding_day3_checked (boolean)\n\n**PostgreSQL table: onboarding_progress**\nColumns: contact_id, profile_complete (bool), first_import_done (bool), first_integration_done (bool), first_report_done (bool)\n\n**Env variables:** PRODUCT_NAME\n\n**Extend the journey:** Copy the Wait → Check Milestones → Email section and set to 168hrs (Day 7) and 336hrs (Day 14) for the full onboarding arc.",
